Flight
  Flight type = limb-with-flight strength * limb-with-flight level - body wgt
    Unlimited flight
    Limited flight (ranging from 2 turns to 10)
    Slow your fall

Armor
  Max damage reduction

Encumbrance
  Reduction to speed/dexterity; often paired with armor

Evasion
  Bonus to dodge

Auto attack
  What type of damage? fire, ice, impale, etc
  How much damage?
  Chance to hit?

